IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. ALTER-COMPUTABLE-BECOMES-NORMAL.

DATA DIVISION.
01 TARGET-FIELD PICTURE IS X(30).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MOVE "ORIGINAL-COMPUTED" TO TARGET-FIELD
ALTER ROUTE TO PROCEED TO ALTERED-NORMAL
MOVE "COMPUTED-FIELD" TO TARGET-FIELD
GO TO ROUTE.

ROUTE.
GO TO TARGET-FIELD.

ORIGINAL-COMPUTED.
DISPLAY "ORIGINAL COMPUTED TARGET"
STOP.

COMPUTED-FIELD.
DISPLAY "COMPUTED FIELD TARGET"
STOP.

ALTERED-NORMAL.
DISPLAY "ALTERED NORMAL TARGET"
STOP.
